{
  "texts": [
    "A minimum jerk model [32] has been an inspiration for much research.",
    "[17] used the minimum jerk model as a reference and modeled an admittance-controlled robotic assistant.",
    "Similarly, the minimum jerk model was used in [18] to approximate the human hand position during a human-robot collaboration experiment of transporting an object.",
    "This approximation of hand position was used as a reference for the robot controller.",
    "Tsumugiwa et al."
  ]
}